{{#system~}}
Analyze the provided `Google Maps Restaurant Reservation URL` in the <ProvidedGoogleMapsReservationURL> block.
Validate and transform it according to <ExplicitConstraints> and <OutputFormat> rules.

---

<ExplicitConstraints alt="explicit constraints">
If <ProvidedGoogleMapsReservationURL> block contains something which does not look like a valid `Google Maps Restaurant Reservation URL`:
  - Set `input_google_maps_reservation_url_is_valid` as `false`
  - Set `output_refined_transformed_google_maps_reservation_url` as "null"
  - Set `output_google_maps_restaurant_id` as "null"
Examples for invalid `Google Maps Restaurant Reservation URL`:
  - `https://www.google.com/maps/reserve/v/dine/c/` (missing `XXXXXXXXXXX` part)
  - `https://www.google.com/maps/XXXXXXXXXXX/` (missing `/reserve/` part)
  - `example.com` (domain other than `google.com/maps/reserve`)
Examples for valid `Google Maps Restaurant Reservation URL`:
  - `https://www.google.com/maps/reserve/v/dine/c/XXXXXXXXXXX`
  - `https://www.google.com/maps/reserve/dine?c=XXXXXXXXXXX&ihs=3`
  - `https://www.google.com/maps/reserve/v/dine/c/XXXXXXXXXXX?source=pa&opi=79508299&hl=en-US&gei=FXdYZ4OeLcTm5NoProiP4Qk&sourceurl=http://www.google.com/service/MapsPlaceService/GetPlace?hl%3Den%26authuser%3D0%26gl%3Dus`
  - `google.com/maps/reserve/v/dine/c/XXXXXXXXXXX` (without `https://www.` or similar)
</ExplicitConstraints>

---

<OutputFormat alt="rules regarding output format">
1. The output must be a valid JSON object generated according to provided schema.
2. `output_refined_transformed_google_maps_reservation_url`:
  - Must be a valid URL without any additional redundant query parameters or "null"
  - Must be transformed to the following format: `https://www.google.com/maps/reserve/v/dine/c/XXXXXXXXXXX`:
    - E.g. `https://www.google.com/maps/reserve/dine?c=XXXXXXXXXXX&ihs=3` -> `https://www.google.com/maps/reserve/v/dine/c/XXXXXXXXXXX`
3. `output_google_maps_restaurant_id` must be a valid `Google Maps Restaurant ID` (e.g. `XXXXXXXXXXX`) or "null"
</OutputFormat>

